{
  "stem": "13219.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, from Berezne.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe a few of them was from a different city, but most of them from Berezne.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which, we knew each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, we used to steal whatever we could at night in farms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A chicken, whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we hear that if they catch you-- the Ukrainian people, if they bring a Jew to the authorities they used to pay him with a pound of salt, because salt was very, very scarce in there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So at that time, they used to pay a pound of salt for a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not all of them were bad, but there was some of them which were very bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that point, we heard that the partisans are not far from us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally, after three or four weeks-- I think four weeks-- we met up with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were speaking Russian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were an outfit-- came down from Moscow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when were there for about a month or so with them, I remember we came down-- they made two big fires on each side for about 500 feet, and we had a plane from Moscow come down and bring some ammunition and a doctor, and take some-- they had a couple of wounded people to take back.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were soldiers, trained as partisans, and parachute down to the Ukraine and to arrest, and do whatever they can there to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were with them for over eight months, until they took a lot-- they took in a lot of people at the time-- kids, women with children-- and they couldn't operate whatever they had to do.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
